{"type": "article", "id": 23811, "title": "可旋转的灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-14T07:00:23Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 21, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702143358vZWyNijUKHXBImut.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一盏可旋转的灯，球形灯体在漏斗形的灯座上。它由两个玻璃球体组成，一个是完全透明的，另一个带有一半的颜色。当旋转球形灯体时，不透明的一半形成了灯罩，遮住了一部分光源，使其方向和角度都不相同，有间接调整光线大小的作用。另外，球形灯体，漏斗形灯座和圆柱形灯座这些不同的几何图形搭配在一起，很可爱，<a href=\"http://www.moritzputzier.com/inti\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143356N3l0dQbcoIkLph5v.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.56203704\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143356hyfmXjUMorIVwAB0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70293399\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021433571uU5fzpShgob2r6R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49877751\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143357HgoCqdKbWOf9n8hT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49877751\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}